      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "I don't care how you create the GDS. If your GDS is clean by the precheck, then it should be good. \n\nYou licensing/legal agreements with proprietary vendors/foundries might cause you issues. I don't provide legal advice, talk to your lawyer \uD83D\uDE42\n\nI also don't know anyone doing this so the likelihood of hitting bugs or edge cases is also very high. We also don't provide any type of support for their tooling.",
